### --- Workspace Endpoints ---

### 1. Create Workspace
POST {{baseUrl}}/deploy/workspace
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{workspaceName}}",
  "cacheName": "{{cacheName}}"
}

### 2. Get Workspace Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/deploy/workspace/{{workspaceName}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 3. List Agents in Workspace
GET {{baseUrl}}/deploy/workspace/{{workspaceName}}/agents
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 4. Delete Workspace
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deploy/workspace/{{workspaceName}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### --- Agent Endpoints ---

### 5. Create Agent
POST {{baseUrl}}/deploy/agent/{{workspaceName}}/{{agentName}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 6. Get Agent Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/deploy/agent/{{workspaceName}}/{{agentName}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 7. Delete Agent
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/deploy/agent/{{workspaceName}}/{{agentName}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### --- Deployment Endpoints (Placeholders) ---

### 8. Create Deployment
POST {{baseUrl}}/deploy/deployment/{{workspaceName}}/{{agentName}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 9. Get Deployments for Agent
GET {{baseUrl}}/deploy/deployment/{{workspaceName}}/{{agentName}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 10. Get Deployment by UUID
GET {{baseUrl}}/deploy/deployment/{{deploymentUuid}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### 11. Get Deployment by Index
GET {{baseUrl}}/deploy/deployment/{{workspaceName}}/{{agentName}}/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
